{
  "summary": "Implemented measurement-unit selection support for feed-type pricing while preserving kilograms as the internal/storage base. Feed-type form, listing, and CSV export now follow the selected feeding unit, precision handling was centralized in shared currency/measurement helpers, backend feed-type export gained optional measurementUnit support, and coverage was added. Commit: d4e8965. Verified with Maven tests for FeedTypeServiceTest and FeedTypeControllerContractTest, the frontend export-context node test, and a frontend build. A pre-existing eslint warning remains in FeedTypePage, and unrelated local workspace/generated files were left unstaged.",
  "changed_files": [
    "backend/farmapp/src/main/java/com/jpsoftware/farmapp/feed/controller/FeedTypeController.java",
    "backend/farmapp/src/main/java/com/jpsoftware/farmapp/feed/service/FeedTypeService.java",
